<MELItem itemNbr="21-61-03" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-21-61-03.1.2-21-61-03">
<Title>Flight Deck Zone Air Temperature Sensor System</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>At least one air conditioning pack operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Trim air pressure regulator valve associated with operating pack operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Flight deck zone duct temperature sensor system associated with operating pack operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Flight deck zone trim valve associated with operating pack operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceNote>
<Para>For an air conditioning pack to be operating normally, certain items associated with that system must operate normally.  See MEL item 21-51-01 for a list of those items.</Para>
</MaintenanceNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
